products.name: Water-repellent puffer gilet
products.description: Lightly padded bomber jacket in nylon. Loose fit fit with a ribbed, stand-up collar and a zip down the front. Flap side pockets and two inner pockets with a concealed press-stud, and a zipped sleeve pocket. Wide ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Lined.

products.name: Regular Fit Hoodie
products.description: Top in sweatshirt fabric with a double-layered drawstring hood, kangaroo pocket and wide ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.

products.name: Fitted jacket
products.description: Fitted jacket in woven fabric with notch lapels and a single button fastening at the front. Jetted front pockets, a decorative button at the cuffs and a single back vent. Lined.

products.name: Pleated chiffon dress
products.description: Calf-length dress in crêpe chiffon with gathers at the front and back and a round neckline with a small opening and a concealed button at the front. Short raglan sleeves, covered elastication at the waist and a flared, pleated skirt. Lined.

products.name: Pleated satin skirt
products.description: Ankle-length pleated skirt in satin with a slight sheen. Loose fit with a high, elasticated waist and a high slit at each side. Overlocked hem. Unlined.

products.name: Wide trousers
products.description: Tailored, loose-fitting trousers in woven fabric. High waist with concealed elastication and a zip fly. Diagonal side pockets and fake welt back pockets. Wide, straight legs with pleats at the front.

products.name: Draped dress
products.description: Short, sleeveless dress in jersey with an elegant, asymmetric neckline and pleats at one side of the waist to create a gently draped effect.

products.name: Gathered bodycon dress
products.description: Fitted, calf-length, sleeveless dress in soft jersey. Small stand-up collar and a concealed zip on one shoulder. Gathers at the waist for a gently draped effect and a straight-cut hem. Unlined.

products.name: Knot-detail top
products.description: Fitted top in heavy jersey made from a viscose blend. Asymmetric neckline with a knot detail, a cut-out section at the front and long sleeves. Partly lined.

products.name: Double-breasted blazer
products.description: Loose-fit, double-breasted blazer in woven fabric with notch lapels and buttons at the front. Welt chest pocket, welt front pockets with a flap, and a single back vent. Decorative buttons at the cuffs. Lined.

products.name: Cropped turtleneck top
products.description: Cropped, sleeveless top in jersey with a turtleneck. Fitted style with gathered side seams for a gently draped effect.

products.name: Wide trousers
products.description: Trousers in woven fabric made from recycled polyester with a high waist, concealed hook-and-eye fastener, zip fly and wide, straight legs with creases.

products.name: Plissé wrap dress
products.description: Short plissé dress in woven fabric with a V-shaped neckline. Wrapover front with narrow ties at one side and a concealed button at the other. Long sleeves with gathers over the shoulders and covered elastication at the cuffs. Partly lined.

products.name: Dark grey/Snakeskin-patterned
products.description: Cardigan in sweatshirt fabric with a soft brushed inside. Round neckline with a frill-trimmed Peter Pan collar, dropped shoulders, press-studs down the front, open front pockets and long sleeves.

products.name: Collared cardigan
products.description: Cardigan in sweatshirt fabric with a soft brushed inside. Round neckline with a frill-trimmed Peter Pan collar, dropped shoulders, press-studs down the front, open front pockets and long sleeves.

products.name: Oversized baseball jacket
products.description: Oversized baseball jacket in sweatshirt fabric with a soft brushed inside and a print motif at the front. Ribbed stand-up collar, press-studs down the front and dropped shoulders. Ribbing at the cuffs and hem.

products.description: Jeans in cotton denim with an all-over print and a relaxed fit through the hip, thigh and leg. Elasticated paper bag waist, fake fly with a button, diagonal side pockets and tapered legs.

products.name: Printed T-shirt
products.description: Loose-fit shirt in a cotton weave with a print motif at the back and an embroidered motif on the chest pocket. Collar, buttons down the front, dropped shoulders, and long sleeves with buttoned cuffs. Rounded hem that is slightly longer at the back.

products.name: Printed hoodie
products.description: Loose-fit hoodie in lightweight sweatshirt fabric with a cheerful all-over print. Lined hood with a wrapover front, dropped shoulders and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.

products.name: Wide Leg Low Jeans
products.description: 5-pocket jeans in cotton denim with print motifs. Regular fit through the hip and thigh with wide legs. Low, adjustable, elasticated waist and a zip fly and button.

products.name: Relaxed Straight Fit Jeans
products.description: 5-pocket jeans in washed cotton denim with print motifs on the legs. Relaxed fit through the hip and thigh with straight legs. Adjustable, elasticated waist and a fake fly and button.

products.name: Patterned cotton dress
products.description: Dress in soft cotton jersey with an all-over print. Round neckline with a narrow trim and long sleeves.

products.name: Motif-detail zip-through hoodie
